::Zardus::

Zardus looks down at some scanner reports, watching the Oblitercons 
fly off toward the ship. He frowns, watching Predacon signatures do 
the same.

"Alliance members heading for the platform," he says into his comm-
link, "Abort the attack. The Oblitercons might need backup at their 
destination, go to their coordinates." He ends the transmission, 
sending the coordinates of Vehemoth's ship.

Zardus looks up from his comp as Delta exits the ship, looking the 
bot over.

"Ah, good to see you, Delta," he says, looking around.

"Nemesis, Unitron, we need to set up the underwater defences. Please 
report to me at once."
